text: Yvonne Schnorf-Wabe (born 28 July 1965) is a road cyclist from Switzerland. She represented her nation at the 1996 Summer Olympics and 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Cyclingarchives.com Category:Swiss female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Switzerland Category:Living people Category:People from Meilen District Category:1965 births
